A little about me...

I am interested in the mathematical analysis of deep learning methods, as well as pursuing first principle approaches to modeling nature. Following these interests I am slowly climbing out of the Dunning-Kruger Valley of Despair after swapping synthetic biological research for mathematical enlightenment.
